main event: An unidentified flying object was sighted in Economy, Pennsylvania on May 27, 1965, observed for approximately 90 seconds.
interesting points: The object was described as round or circular in shape and silent in operation,The object exhibited glowing white color with 5 or 6 small fins or protrusions,Observers initially thought it was a shooting star but later recognized it as a rotating glowing object, The sighting occurred around 9:30 PM during Daylight Saving Time, The object appeared to travel at high speed, accelerating and decelerating intermittently.
sighted object: a round or circular object with glowing white color and protrusions
